lilo-installer (0.0.2) unstable; urgency=low

  * Add Brazilian Portuguese debconf template.
  * Add Danish debconf template.
  * Drop depend on chroot.  There is no such package.
  * Fall back to using /proc/mounts if /etc/mtab doesn't exist
  * Translate from devfs names to old-style names.
  * Put -boot as maintainer, put moshez and me in Uploaders.
  * Convert to po-debconf, set Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 4.1.13)
    to ensure that generated templates are right, and set output encoding
    to UTF-8.

